latestPosts.caption:
Beyoncé x Balmain
@beyonce wears custom Balmain by @olivier_rousteing for the Cowboy Carter Tour on June 22nd in Paris. Inspired by the Statue of Liberty, the look is sculpted from foam and wrapped in green leather to emulate the appearance of flowing draped fabric. Hand-painted shading and patina add a lifelike, aged finish - echoing the iconic monument itself.

@lindsaylohan featured in @elleusa.
Wearing Balmain Pre-Fall 2025 by @olivier_rousteing.
